nts.','2023-12-15',33,' Documentary Music',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eqbUSMNlrg3bcAarU24ndcvtBK5.jpg',''),(3053,'Baby Boy, Baby Girl','Josie is a failed startup businesswoman, who is struggling with no permanent job. Ever since she saw her ex-boyfriend Seb escorting a politician and broke up with him three years ago, Josie remains single. Seb, on the other hand, becomes more sophisticated from earning handsomely through Sugar Dating. Josie learns about Seb’s success, prompting her to ask Seb to groom her for Sugar Dating. Once Josie gets a grasp on the work, she will be good at what she does and will not struggle financially anymore. At the same time, Seb’s feelings for her start coming back, but Josie now sees love differently. She thinks that love should only be transactional. It does not help that Josie can’t forget the time when Seb broke her heart.','2023-03-22',107,' Drama',1,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1TVQP2KuC7b5xYTsGrYy335SG3I.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5pP3kpWWPJrtIafL0o5lxOova7N.jpg'),(3054,'Here Love Lies','In the pursuit of \'love and forever\', single parent and Travel Blogger Amanda, embarks on a social media romance with American TourGuide Michael. A trip to the US to meet up for the first time, opens up more doors than both anticipated.','2023-03-03',131,' Romance Thriller',4,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9T6RD2i3aI8PXjGEcj07xTQetcs.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/j0wpVDBAcViC26NMSvehzOCkeV8.jpg'),(3055,'Various Geeks','','2023-10-28',0,' Comedy Crime',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ppEmwsshPk0A1fRowB6zx4dbJwo.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oYIhOIXd0mAvPmzsQFAgIjsvxBK.jpg'),(3056,'All Good 3 Dead or Alive','This fast paced farce begins with an apparently innocuous request from a village elder to take a recently deceased man to his home village for proper burial. Salim, the simple village man on which this request is bestowed, is afraid of death and by extension dead people, but he reluctantly agrees to take the dead man in his truck in order to incur good-will.','2023-12-22',102,' Comedy',0,'',''),(3057,'Jochen Otten - Zijn stinkende best','','2023-12-29',0,' Comedy',0,'',''),(3058,'ROYGBIV (before the end, the lights shine bright)','A meditative portrait of blue hour & the urban constructions that frame it, “ROYGBIV (before the end, the lights shine bright)” observes modes of connective and enforced time-keeping through human-made infrastructures gridding the sky & ground such as street lights, trains, and electrical cabling. Through rhythmic editing and a score built from harmonizing vocalizations with the hum of electrical transformers, the film contemplates the ways in which human interventions create, harmonize with, and disrupt the cycles of the earth’s rotation and the way living beings exist within it.','2023-12-29',16,'',0,'',''),(3059,'Lot\'s son','“Lot’s Son” is structured in a series of blurry shots, often almost abstract that move along associated with the music, creating a flow of images that transports the viewer into a poetic-visual discourse of great intensity.','2023-12-29',15,'',0,'',''),(3060,'Chandramukhi 2','A wealthy family moves into the Vettaiyapuram palace to renovate their ancestral temple and perform a pooja, unaware of that it will reawaken the feud between a classical dancer, Chandramukhi and Vettaiyan Raja from centuries ago.','2023-09-28',158,' Comedy Drama Horror',3.7,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3OT9dFROPL4t53tt3WQ4rl033zC.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5YnMSiaIYALebC2YDae2mgqCAuV.jpg'),(3061,'The Wedding Contract','Rebecca, a teacher, and Adam, an ad executive are excited to plan their Jewish wedding, but their wedding and future are put into jeopardy when Adam lands a new ad campaign, and their mothers meet for the first time.','2023-06-17',84,' TV Movie Comedy Romance',5.7,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qRf0OkF7QcwwYmP4thgnU7ArZet.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/k4GU1ABRhoOU0l2YCiQ9fuvHXNC.jpg'),(3062,'A Business Proposal HK','Career-oriented CEO of Go Food, Keung Tai Mo Tyson, agrees to go on a blind date his grandfather set up for him. Meanwhile, Suen Ho Lee Hollie, a small fry in Go Food, agrees to go on a blind date in her best friend Chan Ying Shu\'s stead. A love story between the big boss and a low-ranking employee begins with this blind date. On the other hand, Tyson\'s secretary Cheung Shing Dong Frankie and Chan Ying Shu, a rich man\'s daughter, fall in love at first sight. The two will experience many unforgettable moments as their relationship develops in this romantic comedy.','2023-11-27',675,' Romance Comedy',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aZKqX1GNRhzSsDSJsgVl4t3Gsqh.jpg',''),(3063,'Gavyn’s Fall of Kabul','Forced to flee his college town in a desperate bid to stay employable, our protagonist must leave everything he knows behind, including his car. Six months later, he returns to retrieve it, embarking on a treacherous journey across a war-torn landscape.  As he navigates the chaos and destruction left in the wake of a conflict that has torn California apart, he must face his own demons and find the strength to keep going; but when disaster strikes and a radiator hose breaks, he is plunged into a fight for survival that will test his will and determination to the limit.  In this stunning tale of resilience and courage, witness the true cost of dropping out of college and the power of the human spirit to overcome even the greatest of obstacles.','2023-12-29',56,' Documentary Adventure Thriller',0,'',''),(3064,'WERDE, DER DU BIST','','2023-12-29',0,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/o6s58iYzsX4oQAYUe2Md8ntubQu.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rAKB02kHp1e9mfAyDx5Jbr1NMru.jpg'),(3065,'Rayen Panday - Trigger','','2023-12-29',0,' Comedy',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tbPdnBDfO6Ff8PQFKP2JwwmWspk.jpg',''),(3066,'Stepdaddy Fucked My Ass','Stepdaddy Fucked My Ass','2023-07-06',114,'',10,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/l7Ar3e5ZT9huqaR9hX