fore volunteer patients report having unexpected erections - fast forward ten years and word of the adverse side effect has travelled from Wales to New York resulting in Viagra’s first release in 1998 with orders soon exceeding predictions.  What follows is the big story of the little blue pill.','2023-12-08',89,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bIkPzNiK8ODbgAPxPaKz5KQbnjq.jpg',''),(7363,'The Kennedy Dynasty','The story of a powerful political and economic dynasty, fundamental to understanding the turbulent destiny of the United States of America throughout the 20th century; of nine brothers who had truly extraordinary lives, marked by both greatness and tragedy: the story of the Kennedy family.','2023-07-02',90,' Documentary History TV Movie',7.5,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/efWfz7cFUAQ0DQ9jJA6eFVNlBp7.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kzaKOyA65RBeC50UN61qahS9f1h.jpg'),(7364,'Animelo Summer Live 2022 -Sparkle- DAY2','','2023-03-29',0,' Music',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rWD2dvLMZJHSsUTDCNJh5QK2dhu.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/88m8onjIDCjM3YFUyBhracCONoy.jpg'),(7365,'hololive 4th fes. Our Bright Parade Day 2','Our Bright Parade is hololive\'s musical concert portion of the SUPER EXPO 2023.  As with the previous fes concert, this will be fully 3D Augmented Reality, with talent moving around the stage and accompanied by a live band. This year has been described as \"a nonstop shiny stage where anyone can join the parade anytime, regardless of generation and boundary\".','2023-03-19',180,' Animation Music',10,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lym4tAMIKuCBVeQsSM7eJigDCdF.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2SaDxgTNNrWL1pvDIxTRdUKHvqj.jpg'),(7366,'Slow Burn','After an accident, a firefighter must extinguish terrifying trauma as he attempts to reignite his career.','2023-09-06',13,' Drama Thriller',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/inhK0k78eRYDdCHZ0bzhj8gv70t.jpg',''),(7367,'The Accident','Joana is the victim of a hit-and-run after antagonizing an aggressive driver who cut her off in traffic. On the surface, she’s visibly shaken but manages to walk away unscathed. Intending to shrug it off alongside her partner Cecília, a viral video turns up online, forcing her to process the event. Reluctantly the pair enter the lives of culprit Elaine, her estranged husband Cléber and son Maicon, an introverted budding filmmaker.','2023-08-24',95,' Drama',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ief6Xf2T9pN1d6XCfNteCCwTDUY.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1jZJivVRpKvxLokmdMsrAd5byhn.jpg'),(7368,'Cwiar Cymru','Providing a voice for queer people in rural West Wales','2023-12-08',5,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4OVWU9wTlPcSmofjZek2wvabGwT.jpg',''),(7369,'Valóság.exe: A színfalak mögött','','2023-12-08',0,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qYxXJpKc72iF9bCqU0Vq3i6MIHU.jpg',''),(7370,'NIGHTLIFE','Vincent navigates a dark city, on his way to make one last delivery. A short crime thriller made by two film students.','2023-12-08',3,' Crime Thriller',0,'',''),(7371,'Glory to the Heroes','An eye-opening documentary capturing Ukrainian soldiers in trenches and civilians facing ongoing destruction by invading Russian military forces.','2023-12-08',89,' Documentary War',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/e1OuOiLwighf0f6a88t0UN5z7et.jpg',''),(7372,'The Black Saint and The Sinner Lady','A hitman is seduced by a dancer that he had been tasked to kill.','2023-12-08',4,' Drama Crime Science Fiction',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/d4lwDCSy2sKWPsDIbu0S0Trbf0K.jpg',''),(7373,'Fight for the Token: The Secret Woman','Yuan Bin is a member of the Jinyiwei (Brocade Guards) and is ordered by Commander Ji Men Da to track down a military talisman. Yuan Bin leads his brothers in the Jinyiwei to victory against Mongolian mercenaries. Just when Yuan Bin is about to get the talisman, a figure brushes past and snatches it away. This figure is the Golden Sword Sect\'s master, Tranquility. Yuan Bin chased after her and fought with Tranquility. As a result, Tranquility used a demonic spell and managed to escape. At the same time, Ji Men Da attacked the Golden Sword Sect, tortured them and found seven talismans. Together with the four talismans that Ji Men Da had hidden, he had eleven talismans in his possession. It turns out that Ji Menda is the one who wants the talisman the most. By coincidence, Yuan Bin and Tranquility found the last talisman at the bottom of the cliff, they escaped and looked for a chance to kill Ji Men Da. The twelve talismans are finally complete!','2023-04-27',97,' Action',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vyBzzXXz2RltiP9G0IHnaPPZFeI.jpg',''),(7374,'Shyamchi Aai','An adaptation of social worker and freedom fighter Sane Guruji\'s autobiographical novel Shyamchi Aai.','2023-11-10',0,' Drama Family',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ospWAjehyxFPePxWTTJyZXuWMZv.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sVGoVj0FCR0ZTHq68bWRh0pO0xp.jpg'),(7375,'Interface','Two sisters who tragically lose their father now attempt to bring their estranged mother back from a coma by getting into her mind by finding and using a machine a that interfaces across multiple dimensions.','2023-03-28',111,' Science Fiction Thriller',3,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nWCiXbL62Xy23TPsOKzxp0ernkc.jpg',''),(7376,'Is There Anybody Out There?','While navigating daily discrimination, a filmmaker who inhabits and loves her unusual body searches the world for another person like her, and explores what it takes to love oneself fiercely despite the pervasiveness of ableism.','2023-11-17',87,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qrXxDgWQVXT51wM74Y4TeM4IyRx.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/q4TTu9KqpsW7kn7goqN4Czcddgy.jpg'),(7377,'Abracatabras','','2023-12-15',0,' Comedy',0,'',''),(7378,'Bucha','The story of a refugee from Kazakhstan who in the spring of 2022 saved hundreds of Ukrainians in Bucha and other cities and towns occupied by Russian troops.','2023-12-08',120,'',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wcO9fbhoclMljnWOJEWiK0kGePF.jpg',''),(7379,'Rainer Sarnet’s The Invisible Fight','As a portrayal of artistic process, the film examines the inner workings of a film director’s mind with the aim to understand Sarnet’s own invisible fight. We follow the journey of an endangered species called Estonian film director.','2023-12-08',29,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kYz0AC5HTfki1glHKh2EzY8Nb9h.jpg',''),(7380,'A Father\'s Promise','The story of professional musician Mark Barden, whose story of his life changed dramatically when his son Daniel was killed at Sandy Hook Elementary School.','2023-12-08',0,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3skkShxBnq9xmR63ox08E3k3CxX.jpg',''),(7381,'Pressure Makes Diamonds','When all the other kids in Port Chester, NY went outside to play after school, young Anthony Valbiro raced to his basement rec room...to grab a microphone, turn on the reel-to-reel and croon his heart out.  In this film, based on an autobiographical one-man play of the same name, Anthony draws us into the \"quest for fame\" that was his 1960s childhood.  Along the way, we ponder questions about how the people who raise us shape us, what constitutes \"success\" and at what cost do we pursue our deepest dream.','2023-09-08',0,'',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8uMAiVD6lsDkWevXxiIGu5az6ZQ.jpg',''),(7382,'Hell\'s Stoker','A portrait film about Seaküla Simson, one of the sculptors with the best sense of form in Estonia. It is impossible for a man who went through the war in Afghanistan to forget what he experienced. Again and again the past catches up with him. Even in dreams. The only way to face your demons is to make fun of them.','2023-09-08',77,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/old23ydun5UifAP0CjIKRT7Rwf5.jpg',''),(7383,'The Homecoming','Sámi artefacts from the Finnish National Museum are returning home to Sápmi, while the holy drums of the Sámi people are still imprisoned in the basements of museums across Europe. The returning objects symbolise the dignity, identity, history, connection to ancestors and a whole world view that was taken from the Sámi people. Director Suvi West takes the viewer behind the scenes of the museum world to reflect on the spirit of the objects, the inequality of cultures and the colonialist burden of museums.','2023-09-08',75,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7BXNEcTDtiDxzbkRIFHiH4OLPt6.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8h8LQkPXIYhiLSSxO4act1Lw3ZK.jpg'),(7384,'Sansón and Me','Borders have defined Sansón’s life. There’s the physical and psychological border between Mexico and the US. And now, looking at a life behind bars, there’s the one that separates him from his loved ones. Since it is forbidden to film inside the jail, Reyes recreates Sansón’s life – with the help of his family – through letters and by casting an untrained actor to play his friend. The resulting film is a reflection on migration, the notion of family, what it means to see one’s life on film, and the harshness and injustice of the US prison system.','2023-03-03',83,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ubAVA3hatW3uq549tNQUlrZgzjt.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wnNM8nZkLhAeQJ4YjOPBoGj7PgN.jpg'),(7385,'One Summer','For more than 25 years, Marc Côté, street chaplain and parish priest, has lived with the poor and the homeless. Today, Marc is a worn-out man. Exhausted from running his church, which serves as a shelter, and overwhelmed by the bills they can no longer pay, Marc must face the facts: he will have to shut down his church. Like a call from Providence, he inherits a property in the Bas-du-Fleuve region and decides to take a group of homeless people with him, who, like himself, need a vacation.','2023-07-14',126,' Drama Comedy',7.4,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/33KGCpaAbqH5SMIV7koQo7Fjt3M.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/baAVGkUGfpbk6wkRB4uiLxFC5MV.jpg'),(7386,'After Hours','A college student encounters something strange while studying late as she discovers she may not be alone.','2023-12-14',3,' Horror',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1hdZu6uk4LNeUL4dXJttHCeUfUb.jpg',''),(7387,'Fight For Justice','Baai Ji, a generous man devoted to social work, takes on the responsibility of finding a missing girl when police refuse to act and help her mother.','2023-11-21',0,' Drama Crime',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p3NlFaARMqu3wGFn5gfgBYpxPJj.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eUY9ajST9hYmpYWe4kXDCQ68RHd.jpg'),(7388,'????? ???: ??? ???? ?? ??????','The film is about inspiration, reminding the power of collective action, the importance of preserving the heritage of Santa Ana, and the boundless potential that lies within the community. It is a story that deserves to be told, a story that will resonate with audiences of all ages and backgrounds.','2023-11-21',36,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ynAYW8NJBSPZPDVodg9FfnRtZ2U.jpg',''),(7389,'How to Come Alive with Norman Mailer','Norman Mailer, a towering figure in American literature, had a life that was certainly stranger than fiction. From his formative years in Brooklyn, through his career as a preeminent cultural voice, we follow Mailer’s life through 6 marriages, 9 children, 11 bestselling books and 2 Pulitzer Prizes as he solidifies his place in the literary pantheon. With access to Mailer’s family and never before seen footage, this biography details the life and times of an American icon.  (DOC NYC description)','2023-11-21',100,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dnGeoAGj5cBNzavaOdjn5IzHodM.jpg',''),(7390,'Assimilation','After the death of her best friend, Liz attends Julie\'s funeral gathering where strange events begin to occur.','2023-06-02',13,' Horror Thriller',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lLL1bMNlE3zsWdrZ7RDOTW1wFoL.jpg',''),(7391,'THE MYSTERY DAY～有名人連続失踪事件の謎を追え～','','2023-10-07',0,' Mystery',5,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tiNbGeyJmwr0UNR7eALOYS0G6gz.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kGLr6a6Xt6tu7giMqUkhS5yuHbS.jpg'),(7392,'Níobe','In the Brazilian thriller Níobe, Rita (Barbara França) and a group of six other luxury call girls are hired by an important businessman to entertain the guests of an important business meeting for one night.  The purpose of the meeting - which includes the presence of a president of the republic and its main general - is to bribe an opposition deputy to obtain approval for mineral exploration in indigenous territory.  However, the plan does not go as expected and, after all, the future of the country may be in the hands of the seven call girls.','2023-09-07',0,' Thriller Drama',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uD9oiKoFNz6h75yiIlBHjf21Qj8.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aP28BFdJhug1oJAM03QNqZX6SRS.jpg'),(7393,'Cross The Battlefield','The former e-sports veteran didn\'t want his son to repeat his mistakes, so the two had a fierce quarrel. During the quarrel father was shocked by an electricity, and his youth returned to his twenties. When he was young, his father found his former comrades-in-arms and formed a team to defeat his son with strength. In the subsequent confrontation with each other, the father gradually discovered his son\'s talent and dream.','2023-07-06',88,' Comedy',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cBShWaY4gG7rago4mXVX8dj7zJJ.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/63WYrnNPa2cJkyG27XdwVxQECE0.jpg'),(7394,'Rahsia','A leisurely picnic takes a tragic turn when Ramlah sees a mysterious figure abducts her son and disappears. Shortly after, she begins encountering unexplained hauntings but her husband doesn`t believe her. But time and time again, clues lead her to believe that her son is close by and still alive, as she races against time to find him before it`s too late.','2023-08-10',90,' Drama Mystery Horror Thriller',10,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fUM8cjJ65yDH0RETDbX6K1YPV6H.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zJjvUXbj6ebbKV3RNer5KQgh5lc.jpg'),(7395,'OVNIS: Les missions secrètes révélées','','2023-12-18',0,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uWbBSfZaaVVglwDVHUGmqcvwuat.jpg',''),(7396,'Eat Your Heart Out','Paolo, an aspiring Italian chef, fresh off of a heartbreak moves from Rome to LA to change his life. To make ends meet he accepts a job as dishwasher at a successful restaurant in Los Angeles, owned by a powerful couple Maya and Chef Carlos. However, the business and the marriage are threatened by a dark secret, could Paolo dream be over that quickly? Paolo\'s kind heart will help him save the restaurant and rescue Maya\'s heart.','2023-11-17',67,' Comedy Romance',3,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aDnhHu9naxeGYD6RbyrlDFTz5ud.jpg',''),(7397,'Green Screen','An amateur film set descends into chaos when a lovers’ quarrel involving a crew member threatens their production.','2023-12-06',29,' Comedy Romance',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ws5B0IRN2V6wwXQTmwTp7IWIDxg.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2422OsIWNn37H2DdFW3zJfu1WKs.jpg'),(7398,'I\'m Perfectly Fine','As a freelance illustrator and perfectionist, Maya’s life is fun fun fun, but also busy busy busy. She perfectly pulls through her work assignments and social activities, thanks to a supportive ‘inner voice’ whom she affectionately calls her ‘Little Motivator’. But when Maya suddenly gets a full-on panic attack and has to slow down for a while, her deepest fear becomes reality: she can no longer be perfect… Maya and her Little Motivator set out to get her back on track ASAP, while struggling to accept that ‘good enough’ might just really be good enough.','2023-11-09',30,' Animation',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fJONIVeLNUQrfserrajG04bMnG7.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/x8IwsbsUrXFhlMkUN35dRcNMriF.jpg'),(7399,'Raaghu','A medicine delivery executive loots the houses he delivers to make quick bucks. One day, a phone call from a stranger forces him to do a series of unlawful activities, failing which he could face dangerous consequences.','2023-04-28',93,' Drama Thriller',7,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ef3bUDv3iU9T3ewHMmGf1sG36g8.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fDzIYEBkH9pdvWrmw823FOv7YOK.jpg'),(7400,'The Dirty 3rd: Next Generation','Twenty years after the incarceration of his son, Street has graduated from drug kingpin to legitimate businessman when his trusted street soldier comes home from prison and his long lost grandson shows up unexpectedly in Houston.','2023-01-16',106,' Crime',2,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4tLq7Wj7XFiLSAUQ2vt2KMqVhOZ.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eeti9n02moAvgxViPwBk9zcLCd.jpg'),(7401,'Paul Muldoon - Laoithe is Lirici','In this bi-lingual “documentary musical” from acclaimed director Alan Gilsenan, the poet Paul Muldoon explores life and language in a series of musical collaborations with a stellar array of artists including Paul Simon, Liam Neeson, PJ Harvey, Bono, Ruth Negga, Paul Brady, Run DMC and Iarla O’Lionáird.','2023-01-29',75,' Documentary',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/49gtV3fHQBUFwg31mlIDTvgaBMV.jpg','');
INSERT INTO `movies` VALUES (7402,'Sunlight','When Leon, a recovering addict, discovers the terminally-ill sponsor he adores is planning to self-euthanise, he feels a sense of betrayal. He begs Iver - the man he sees as a hero - to watch the tribute show he\'s been preparing in his honour.','2023-06-16',95,' Comedy Drama',7,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zqh9ft5m6pLPtBA0Am24mNtBcXf.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/GvurHHCdLzNdvXmmKpc6BQ7APB.jpg'),(7403,'Der NSU-Prozess als Film','','2023-12-20',110,' Documentary',0,'',''),(7404,'CANVAS','Pablo, an introverted child, has the ability to enter his mother\'s paintings, this takes him on a surreal and bizarre journey that dissolves the limits between reality and imagination.','2023-12-06',12,' Horror Thriller',0,'',''),(7405,'Dilemma','Martina and Catalina experience a night that will change their lives forever when they find themselves involved in a harassment situation.','2023-12-06',11,' Drama',0,'',''),(7406,'F I G H T !','A girl, Cabella gets into a fight with a young aggressive, loser of a boy, Levi.','2023-12-06',1,' Action',10,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4JlAxKdK8kcr4mWPWTyUo7bQPyJ.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uB0mV6fOSjpOqONnGONOdqMtMqs.jpg'),(7407,'Istri Boss','','2023-06-12',0,' Drama Romance',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4JYCweGi2fD0t5aBk0Kokcx60UC.jpg',''),(7408,'Come Out in Jesus Name','Following a startling chain of events, the most controversial pastor in America, Greg Locke, took a 180-degree turn from his mainstream religious traditions and led his church to the brink of revival. He and a diverse group of unconventional preachers then began to spark the most important awakening in the history of the Christian Church — through the most unlikely means – by casting out demons. This fiery film documents the beginnings of their journey.','2023-03-13',100,' Drama Documentary Fantasy',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6477EtUdjnPt48CTWF6P6MDTYRX.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500