052,'Ourselves Alone','Inspired by the Northern Bank robbery that took place in Belfast in 2004, Ourselves Alone is set in the house of a bank manager and his wife, who are taken hostage by brother-and-sister IRA members - Aoife and Sean. They plan to force the bank manager to help them carry out the robbery. But when a psychopathic third IRA member - Liam - arrives at the house unexpectedly, things start to go wrong.','2023-11-22',11,' Thriller Crime',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fMb8iqCRyl8nqoFihREh6Paspkx.jpg',''),(9053,'DoubleDown','Inspired by true events, DoubleDown is the story of Ali, a student struggling with money, his relationship and his crippling gambling addiction. Ali promises his girlfriend, Lea, that his next game will be his last and he must fight the temptation to play another round and double down on his chances.','2023-11-25',14,' Drama',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hWZHgtDmQmNTrdYIzM8HaU1yPHV.jpg',''),(9054,'Avulsion','The lives of three women intersect within a tidal of apathy.','2023-08-06',3,'',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7oDvouWBokGSa4lNcRqavJ9pDfv.jpg','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pYomNnyVFBOoUcDVmDTFpKunxpV.jpg'),(9055,'New Beginnings','Will Alun\'s new friendship blossom under the cover of a rugby stand? Abbie is already on side, but Ben is proving a more difficult opposition.','2023-12-14',14,'',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6pOynIlDnB8l4Ik4ttGQg6FYX7L.jpg',''),(9056,'It\'s Nice When People Take the Time to Say Goodbye','Three siblings return to their hometown for the funeral of their beloved uncle Bernard with one hope - to get through the day without any mention of their estranged mother.','2023-12-14',14,' Drama',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uX4thGOthG0ykKUEzeJPMIMuSY9.jpg',''),(9057,'Shedding','Lewis, racked with guilt after attacking the people closest to him, seeks help to delve into his past and regain control of his actions and choices.','2023-11-25',9,' Horror Drama',0,'https://image.tmdb.org/t